Navy SEAL Shooting - Learn How to Shoot From Their Leading Instructor (2015).epub Gooner

Publisher: Center Mass Group, (26 July 2015)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 194378700X
ISBN-13: 978-1943787005

Navy SEAL Shooting is the most complete book ever written about how to shoot a firearm. Written by retired Navy SEAL master firearms instructor, Chris Sajnog this book covers everything you need to know make effective shots in any high-stress situation. Lessons include: mindset and mental training, marksmanship, moving and shooting, malfunctions and every manipulation needed for any semi-automatic pistol or rifle. If you want to learn how to safely and confidently protect your family, this book with 385 pictures and illustrations is all you need
